replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:37:49.000Z","msg":"唔夠人就你係留下儲人數啦, 而家企係到比人圍。冇咁大個頭又要帶咁大頂帽。而家你仲要起車陣封自己後路, 請問如果而家有警察清埸你地仲有冇路走? 有, 就係走入離境禁區然後全部犯哂法比人拉。<br />\n<br />\n而家唯有等多Ｄ人黎幫你, 好被動。唔好起路障, 呢到唔係街"},{"pid":"09a7b929948280737998b34d6bc2f2026428ec9f","tid":1461670,"uid":25617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7c4f0fe08ceb99d8f51078adc9e7d85cd47cf74","tid":1461670,"uid":4349,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a9bc5a43109aa1694e9202813347d78a05a64841","tid":1461670,"uid":25617,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"648b57b93c285a5740c84dd703ab20b368f4cad5","tid":1461670,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:24:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">要講TOPIC都睇到, 推POST唔用721 811 818 講咁多野帶風向呀傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:25:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>黑警死全家 禍必及妻兒</strong></span></span><br />\n然後我係黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:31:42.000Z","msg":"你收皮番屋企抖下好無?<br />\n無腦既抗爭係害緊成百萬人既心血, 你以為講句抗爭就想點就點?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:38:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">你同我含撚啦不如</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"972a007b18b7750a2d2b5eeeaab81212a3bf66f0","tid":1461670,"uid":290804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:38:43.000Z","msg":"咁你想點？"},{"pid":"329955f5f843f5dcfd019be7a2c5e54c32fff951","tid":1461670,"uid":25434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:38:49.000Z","msg":"係啊屌！<br />\n好多鬼<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">禮貌阻機行動開始！</span></span>"},{"pid":"fff750f21b7bf296abd67849c93dfee2648b22f7","tid":146167